name: Rob Banks
description: Rob Banks ($BANKS) is more than a crypto project— it’s a brand that aims to change the financial narrative by combining the power of memes with a real mission: helping ordinary people learn, earn, and build wealth together. Through the Mask, NFTs, blogs, short videos, and interactive experiences, the Banks family co-creates their own financial stories—side by side. Ultimately, Rob Banks proves that when creative storytelling meets innovative technology, anyone can reshape the world of finance for the better.
